channel.title: I'm already logged in?
channel.description:
I found a source I liked for my server, I turned it on, it worked fine, i loved it. I log out, when I try to log back in it says "Your account is already logged in"
So I close, re-compile, then re-run the server. Still says it. So I uninstalled the source, installed it again, still get the error. Wtf happened?[br][br][size=1]Posted on: September 05, 2008, 04:25:06 pm[/size][hr]oh, and it says this for any account i try to log into.
